                    <desc xml:id="abstract-en-134" xml:lang="en">A city north of the <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/202">Tigris</placeName> and east of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/8">Amida</placeName>.</desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="syr-Syrj">
                        <quote source="#bib134-2">ܛܒܝܒܳܐ ܗܘܳܬ ܕܰܡܕܝܢ̈ܬܳܐ ܕܐܳܡܺܝܕ ܠܓܰܪܒܰܝ ܡܰܕܢܚܳܗ̇ ܘܝܰܘܡܳܢ ܩܰܣܛܪܰܐ ܗܝ̣.</quote>
                    </desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="ar">
